setup: A man walked into a hardware store, picked up a can of fly spray and asked the assistant, 'Is this good for wasps?'
punchline: The assistant said, 'no, it kills them'.

setup: When I was ten my Mom told me to take my brother to a movie so she could set up for his surprise birthday party.
punchline: That's when I realized that he was the favorite twin, not me...

setup: My son gave me a huge hug out of nowhere yesterday and it felt amazing
punchline: Until I heard him tell his dad, 'You were right, she is gaining weight!'
